title: No Face Girl, Jeff Foxworthy, and Feits Looks Like a Tomato
description:
Subscribe, rate, and leave a review! -The guys spent the day hiding from the interns at HQ -Top 5 Tuesday: Athlete Photos Outside of Sports -Voicemails Include celebrity chef in prison, mailtime hall of fame, tv characters personality, and lying your way through a career. (01:17:30) No Face Girl joins the show! We discuss Feits' calling out her pillows last year, doing porn as a side gig, whether or not she'll ever show her face, and much more. (01:47:00)Jeff Foxworthy joins the show! He tells us about some of the wild times on the Blue Collar Comedy Tour, his love for hosting tv shows, and we get in a screaming match over the best candy bars and cereal.
